autoconfigd (0.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Reworked the configuration loop so that it tries to configure the interface
    while it's turned down, and if that doesn't work while it's turned up,
    too.

  * Added a little bit of debugging output.

  * Patched paths for the utilities the configuration daemon calls so they're
    Debian-specific.

 -- The Doctor <drwho@virtadpt.net>  Sun, 15 Jun 2014 14:28:41 -0800

